custom_rates.name: usr_HO2NO2_M( temp, c_m )
custom_rates.code:
REAL(KIND=r8) FUNCTION usr_HO2NO2_M( temp, c_m )
! for cesm-consistent reaction labels
! HO2NO2 + M -> HO2+NO2+M
! CESM writes this as dependent on the NO2+HO2 rate
! *** if M is included in reactants, must divide TROEE function by [M]

    REAL(KIND=r8), INTENT(IN) :: temp
    REAL(KIND=r8), INTENT(IN) :: c_m

    usr_HO2NO2_M = TROEE( 4.76e26_r8,10900._r8, 1.8e-31_r8 , 3.2_r8 , &
                          4.7e-12_r8 , 1.4_r8 , TEMP, C_M ) /c_m

END FUNCTION usr_HO2NO2_M

custom_rates.name: usr_MPAN_M( temp, c_m )
custom_rates.code:
REAL(KIND=r8) FUNCTION usr_MPAN_M( temp, c_m )
! for cesm-consistent reaction labels
! MPAN+M -> MCO3+NO2+M

    REAL(KIND=r8), INTENT(IN) :: temp
    REAL(KIND=r8), INTENT(IN) :: c_m

    usr_MPAN_M = 1.2221e17_r8*300._r8*exp( -14000._r8/temp )/(temp*c_m)

END FUNCTION usr_MPAN_M

custom_rates.name: usr_HNO3_OH( temp, c_m )
custom_rates.code:
REAL(KIND=r8) FUNCTION usr_HNO3_OH( temp, c_m )
! for cesm-consistent reaction labels, equivalent to usr5
! HNO3 + OH -> NO3 + H2O

    REAL(KIND=r8), INTENT(IN) :: temp
    REAL(KIND=r8), INTENT(IN) :: c_m

    REAL(KIND=r8) :: k0, k2

   k0 = c_m * 6.5e-34_r8 * exp( 1335._r8/temp )
   k2 = exp( 2199._r8/temp )
   k0 = k0 /(1.0_r8 + k0/(2.7e-17_r8*k2))
   k2 = exp( 460._r8/temp )

   usr_HNO3_OH = k0 + 2.4e-14_r8 * k2

END FUNCTION usr_HNO3_OH

                       1.4e-12_r8 , .7_r8 , TEMP, C_M ) /c_m

custom_rates.name: usr_HO2_HO2( temp, c_m, c_h2o )
custom_rates.code:
REAL(KIND=r8) FUNCTION usr_HO2_HO2( temp, c_m, c_h2o )
! for cesm-consistent reaction labels, equivalent to usr9
! HO2+HO2 -> H2O2+O2
! H2O included in fc calculation, not as reactant

    REAL(KIND=r8), INTENT(IN) :: temp
    REAL(KIND=r8), INTENT(IN) :: c_m
    REAL(KIND=r8), INTENT(IN) :: c_h2o

    REAL(KIND=r8) :: ko, kinf, fc

    if( c_h2o > 0._r8 ) then
       ko   = 2.3e-13_r8 * exp( 600._r8/temp )
       kinf = 1.7e-33_r8 * c_m * exp( 1000._r8/temp )
       fc = 1._r8 + 1.4e-21_r8 *c_h2o* exp( 2200._r8/temp )
       usr_HO2_HO2 = (ko + kinf) * fc
    else
       usr_HO2_HO2 = 0._r8
    end if
END FUNCTION usr_HO2_HO2

custom_rates.name: usr_DMS_OH( temp, c_m )
custom_rates.code:
REAL(KIND=r8) FUNCTION usr_DMS_OH( temp, c_m )
! for cesm-consistent reaction labels, equivalent to usr24
! DMS + OH -> 0.5 SO2 + 0.5 HO2

    REAL(KIND=r8), INTENT(IN) :: temp
    REAL(KIND=r8), INTENT(IN) :: c_m

    REAL(KIND=r8) :: ko, wrk

    wrk   = .21_r8*c_m
    ko    = 1._r8 + 5.5e-31_r8*exp( 7460._r8/temp )*wrk
    usr_DMS_OH = 1.7e-42_r8*exp( 7810._r8/temp )*wrk/ko

END FUNCTION usr_DMS_OH
